Hack Club and @githubeducation have teamed up to give out prizes to teens this summer who build projects!

These are the steps to get started with Arcade!ðŸ•¹ï¸

- Go to hack.af/arcade
- Join the Hack Club Slack
- /hack in #arcade to log your hours!

Hack. Log. Share. Bank. ðŸ•¹ï¸

This summer GitHub and Hack Club are partnering up to bring Arcade to teenagers across the world ðŸŒŽ

how it works:
1. Join the Slack-set your summer project goals.
2. Hack on Projects-every hour you log is a ticket.
3. Get Cool Stuff-exchange your tickets for prizes.

Repeat all summer to earn Bambu 3D printers, Flipper Zeroes, breadboards, MacBooks, Logitech keyboards,
Framework laptops, soldering irons, boba â€¦.. all the stuff you need to make more stuff

ðŸ”—hack.af/arcade
